OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA little showery rain is
OL,6,Fpossible through the middle of the
OL,7,Fday, otherwise mostly dry and bright
OL,8,Fwith sunny spells. Feeling hot and
OL,9,Fhumid, especially in the south and
OL,10,Feast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FRemaining dry and sunny throughout the
OL,14,Fperiod. Feeling hot by day in the
OL,15,Fstrong sunshine and increasingly warm
OL,16,Fand humid overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
